270
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:46,400
Consort, there is your yarn.

271
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:50,500
Aunt Jin-Xi.

272
00:16:50,900 --> 00:16:53,100
Prince Dun beat Zhang-Lin.

273
00:16:53,300 --> 00:16:54,400
What?

274
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:56,000
What are you talking about?

275
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:59,000
Something has happened.

276
00:16:59,100 --> 00:17:00,400
What happened?

277
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:02,600
Prince Dun came back to the capital three days ago.

278
00:17:02,700 --> 00:17:06,400
He was late for the morning assembly, and arrived at the hall in a military uniform.

279
00:17:06,663 --> 00:17:08,253
