293
00:17:42,300 --> 00:17:43,312
What?

294
00:17:43,312 --> 00:17:46,700
Yes, the ancient laws say no one can beat up a censor.

295
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,900
Moreover, it was his fault from the beginning.

296
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:51,300
This time Prince Dun has made everyone angry.

297
00:17:51,600 --> 00:17:55,000
All the censors are calling for him to be punished severely,

298
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,800
