299
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,500
But Prince Dun does not admit any fault.

300
00:17:58,800 --> 00:18:01,100
He hasn't been to assembly for two days, saying he is sick.

301
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:02,600
This is ridiculous.

302
00:18:02,900 --> 00:18:04,700
When His Majesty ascended the throne,

303
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:07,800
everyone knows how he dealt with 8th Prince and 7th Prince.

304
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:10,200
Prince Dun is being disrespectful.

305
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:13,800
I don't this this will be hard for His Majesty to settle.

306
00:18:14,100 --> 00:18:15,800
If His Majesty is truly angry,

307
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:18,000
this is going to become complicated.

308
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:20,700
Prince Dun just made a contribution in the battlefield.

309
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,700
If His Majesty punishes him,

310
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,748
I'm afraid it will affect His Majesty's reputation.

311
00:18:25,900 --> 00:18:27,900
If this doesn't settle out well,

312
00:18:28,131 --> 00:18:30,373
it will harm the Imperial Court.

313
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:31,300
You're right.

314
00:18:31,500 --> 00:18:32,600
Because of this,

315
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:36,500
His Majesty is at the Hall of Mental Cultivation, and hasn't come out all day.

316
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:41,100
