317
00:18:41,800 --> 00:18:44,000
Let me think first.

318
00:19:03,300 --> 00:19:05,145
Greetings, Your Majesty.

319
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:06,900
Wishes for Your Majesty's health and peace.

320
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:07,800
Stand.

321
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:09,700
Thank you, Your Majesty.

322
00:19:16,600 --> 00:19:18,300
You already heard

323
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:21,200
