324
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:24,500
Yes, this news has spread everywhere.

325
00:19:24,800 --> 00:19:28,400
Even as a concubine, I have heard something of it.

326
00:19:28,800 --> 00:19:30,900
Even though there are many matters of state,

327
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:34,300
Your Majesty, you must take care your health.

328
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:38,912
I stewed this donkey-hide gelatin with codonopsis.

329
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:45,600
It's good for Your Majesty, to regulate and reinforce qi.

330
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:52,000
You already know the details

331
00:19:52,300 --> 00:19:53,774
regarding Prince Dun beating up the censor.

332
00:19:54,100 --> 00:19:57,400
What do you think I should do?

333
00:19:58,300 --> 00:20:02,700
Do I need to follow the laws and punish Prince Dun?

334
00:20:02,724 --> 00:20:04,618
Your Majesty is the Emperor.

335
00:20:04,700 --> 00:20:07,100
Of course, Your Majesty needs to follow the laws.

336
00:20:07,500 --> 00:20:09,400
But Your Majesty doesn't need to punish him.

337
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:12,500
I thought you would suggest punishing him.

338
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:14,600
Tell me what you think.

339
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:16,700
Your Majesty won't blame me, if I comment on matters of the state?

340
00:20:16,900 --> 00:20:19,800
It's fine. This is just a normal conversation.

341
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:21,500
I won't blame you.

342
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:23,400
I think

343
00:20:23,600 --> 00:20:26,200
the most important thing right now is to appease the people.

344
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:29,400
And solve the conflict between Prince Dun and the officers.

345
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:32,200
If there's a fight, one side will surely be harmed.

346
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:37,500
But both sides are important assets of the Qing Dynasty.

347
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:40,600
Prince Dun just made a contribution in the battlefield.

348
00:20:40,900 --> 00:20:42,900
If Your Majesty punishes him at this time,

349
00:20:43,100 --> 00:20:46,900
I'm afraid the other generals will become disgruntled.

350
00:20:47,600 --> 00:20:52,700
Actually Your Majesty doesn't need to punish Prince Dun to settle this issue.

351
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:55,600
The officers are angry because

352
00:20:55,800 --> 00:20:57,600
they want a settlement.

353
00:20:57,900 --> 00:21:00,500
Your Majesty just needs to give them a statement.

354
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:06,000
The best way is ask Prince Dun to pay a visit and apologize.

355
00:21:06,300 --> 00:21:09,200
Ask him to apologize?

356
00:21:09,600 --> 00:21:11,400
He is so arrogant,

357
00:21:11,600 --> 00:21:13,500
it'd be easier just to kill him.

358
00:21:13,800 --> 00:21:15,200
Not really.

359
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:18,000
He fought for this country in wars.

360
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:20,000
He's a hero.

361
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:23,400
What is the most difficult obstacle for a hero?

362
00:21:23,800 --> 00:21:26,000
It is a beauty.

363
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:28,000
You clever girl.

364
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:29,900
Only you can think of a trick like this.

365
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:33,000
Your Majesty also knows that a beauty is the most difficult obstacle for a hero.

366
00:21:33,300 --> 00:21:35,400
I don't know anything about big matters.

367
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:40,200
I only know this little trick.

368
00:21:41,100 --> 00:21:42,700
Prince is most afraid of Princess.

369
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:47,300
If Princess helps with this, everything can be settled.

370
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:50,396
I've met the Princess several times.

371
00:21:50,600 --> 00:21:53,400
She is not someone without understanding.

372
00:21:53,900 --> 00:21:58,100
Who do you think should go, and ask for help from the Princess?

373
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:01,000
If Your Majesty doesn't mind,

374
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:04,300
I'd like to take care of this.

375
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:11,000
Among the concubines, you're the one who can help me solve problems.

376
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:15,032
All those officers who take a salary,

377
00:22:15,300 --> 00:22:17,400
just make noise all day,

378
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:20,900
but can't decide whether to punish him or not.

379
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:22,900
They are all useless.

380
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:25,800
I am just one of your concubines.

381
00:22:26,200 --> 00:22:28,600
This is not my idea.

382
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:30,700
It is from Your Majesty.

383
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:33,700
I just guessed correctly, with some luck.

384
00:22:33,900 --> 00:22:36,600
The officers understand books and theories.

385
00:22:36,800 --> 00:22:40,000
But I understand Your Majesty.

386
00:22:40,300 --> 00:22:41,800
His Majesty's thoughts,

387
00:22:42,022 --> 00:22:44,034
I think I can guess at some of them.

388
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:49,900
Huan Huan, only you know what I'm thinking.

389
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:52,900
But look at the behavior of Prince Dun.

390
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:55,700
I can't let him keep doing this.

391
00:22:56,400 --> 00:22:58,288
If Prince Dun continues to be domineering,

392
00:22:58,288 --> 00:23:00,034
Your Majesty will have this for later.

393
00:23:00,300 --> 00:23:02,500
It is really good news for our people.

394
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:06,200
But now is not the time to eliminate Prince Dun.

395
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:09,000
That's right.

396
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:14,000
After all these things are settled,

397
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:18,000
I'm going to let your father take charge of the Censorate.

398
00:23:18,300 --> 00:23:20,500
He can help me impeach all the officers.

399
00:23:20,600 --> 00:23:22,800
But your father alone will not be enough.

400
00:23:22,885 --> 00:23:27,160
The talented officers, not associated with Prince Dun and Nian Gengyao,

401
00:23:27,500 --> 00:23:29,400
I want to promote them all.

402
00:23:29,800 --> 00:23:34,100
I don't want to act rashly, which will only alert the enemy,

403
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:37,200
