404
00:23:37,500 --> 00:23:39,400
To appease them...

405
00:23:39,700 --> 00:23:45,200
Prince Dun and his princess already have a lot of wealth.

406
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:48,400
They are parents now.

407
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:50,200
It seems

408
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:53,100
we need to do something for their children.

409
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:57,400
They have a son and a daughter.

410
00:23:57,800 --> 00:24:00,700
Their daughter is Princess of Qingcheng.

411
00:24:00,719 --> 00:24:04,188
I plan to promote her as He Shuo Princess.

412
00:24:04,600 --> 00:24:07,700
Her position is equal to the the daughter of a concubine.

413
00:24:08,100 --> 00:24:12,900
Then I'll promote his son to Bei Zi, to follow in the footsteps of his father.

414
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:16,300
Your Majesty is considering everything.

415
00:24:16,600 --> 00:24:20,000
But I think Your Majesty must do more than just promote Princess.

416
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:22,400
Her name must be changed as well.

417
00:24:22,700 --> 00:24:26,900
The name should be Gong Ding.

418
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:31,400
