450
00:26:12,600 --> 00:26:15,000
Take care on your way back.

451
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:17,900
I will go.

452
00:26:33,600 --> 00:26:36,900
Young Master, Master An is going that way.

453
00:26:52,200 --> 00:26:54,073
Whoever she is,

454
00:26:54,300 --> 00:26:58,800
