455
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:01,500
Jin-Xi.

456
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:03,900
You, Liu-Zhu and Huan-Bi.

457
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:07,600
Go make preparations for Prince Dun and Princess' arrival to the palace day after tomorrow.

458
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:09,600
Alright.

459
00:27:19,300 --> 00:27:21,073
Greetings, Empress.

460
00:27:21,300 --> 00:27:22,500
Stand.

461
00:27:22,700 --> 00:27:24,600
Thank you, Empress.

462
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:31,600
Greetings, Consort Wan.

463
00:27:33,400 --> 00:27:35,600
Give the seat, and serve the tea.

