486
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:55,400
To educate him properly, so in the future, he can become like his father.

487
00:28:55,500 --> 00:28:58,900
And pacify the nations, and contribute to our country.

488
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:03,100
